Notes
-----

- If `tools/android/.gradle/` appears as unversioned in IDEs, that is local
  Gradle cache noise and not part of the intended source changes.
- If SDK CMake 4 is installed and visible to the script, `cpu-features` may
  fail again. Keep SDK CMake `3.22.1` as the active/available SDK CMake for
  this build.
- If switching machines or paths, forcing rebuild of the enabled dependencies
  is safer than reusing old `prebuilt/*` metadata.
